Demo data notice:

The demo health data included in this repository is synthetic and was created
only for demonstration and reproducibility. It does not contain real patient data,
real medical records, or real personal health information.

Medical safety notice:

ClinDiary is a hackathon prototype and is not a medical device. It does not
diagnose, prescribe medication, change dosages, or replace clinical care.
